high_descs: Turn left to walk into the dining room and face the fridge on the left.
Pick up the knife from the fridge.
Turn left and walk out the room and walk into the bedroom on the left to walk to the nightstand.
Cut the potato on the nightstand into pieces with the knife.
Turn around to exit the bedroom and walk past the table and take a left turn to reach the bathroom to face the sink.
Put the knife on top of the sink.
Head left to exit the room and take a right turn to head to the bedroom to walk to the sidetable.
Pick up a slice of the bread from the nightstand.
Turn around to exit the bedroom and turn right to walk into the dining room to face the microwave on the left.
Heat the slice of potato in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around to exit the dining room and walk to the left to head to the bathroom and face the sink.
Put the slice of potato on the top of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the potato and slice of bread on top of the sink.

high_descs: Enter a room to your left and move in front of the fridge in the corner on the left.
Take the knife from the fridge.
Leave the room and enter the adjacent room on the left, where you walk to a nightstand in the opposite corner.
Using the knife, slice a potato on the nightstand.
Leave the room, continue straight until you reach the wall, and left where you reach an entrance to a bathroom, get in and face the sink.
Place the knife on the sink.
Leave the bathroom, go back in the room with the sidetable, and go to the sidetable.
Pick up a potato from the nightstand.
Leave the room and again go to the adjacent room with the fridge, where you walk to the microwave in the opposite corner.
Place the potato slice in the microwave, heat it up for a bit, then take it out.
Leave the room, head to the bathroom again and face the sink.
Place the potato on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Slice a piece of potato, microwave it and put it on the bathroom sink.

high_descs: Turn left, go to the doorway closer to the book shelf, turn left and go to the fridge.
Pick up the knife in the fridge.
Go to the door and turn left into the room to the left, go to the nightstand beside the pink comforter.
Slice the potato on the dresser.
Go to the door and go across to the wall and turn left, then turn left again in to the bathroom, go to the sink.
Place the knife on the left side of the sink by the handle.
Head back to the potato on the sidetable.
Pick up a slice of the potato from the middle.
Go to the door and turn right into the room beside you, go to the microwave in the corner.
Place the potato slice in the microwave and heat it.
Head back to the bathroom, and go to the sink.
Place the potato on the sink behind the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a potato slice on the counter beside the left faucet handle in the bathroom.
